(2643, 547, '_directions_2_direction', 'field_5aec26cd305c8'),
(2644, 547, 'directions_3_direction', 'Prep your Tortillas. The trick to getting the perfect \"wrap\" for your crunch wrap is this: lie a tortilla on a cutting board. Put a tostada shell in the center of the tortilla and using a knife cut/trace around the circular tostada shell so you get a circular piece of tortilla the same size as the tostada shell. You will need 1 for each crunch wrap you are making.'),
(2645, 547, '_directions_3_direction', 'field_5aec26cd305c8'),
(2646, 547, 'directions_4_direction', 'Once meat and beans are cooked, begin assembly your crunch wraps! Lie 1 large tortilla on a cutting board. Spread some beans in the center and spread about the length of the tostada shell.'),
(2647, 547, '_directions_4_direction', 'field_5aec26cd305c8'),
(2648, 547, 'directions_5_direction', 'Top beans with a layer of cooked meat. Drizzle a layer of queso on top of beans and meat. Place tostada shell in the center on top of meat, beans, queso.'),
(2649, 547, '_directions_5_direction', 'field_5aec26cd305c8'),
(2650, 547, 'directions_6_direction', 'Spread your guacamole on top of the tostada shell, with a layer of sour cream on top of that. Put a spoonful or 2 of pico de gallo on top of that.'),
(2651, 547, '_directions_6_direction', 'field_5aec26cd305c8'),
(2652, 547, 'directions_7_direction', 'Sprinkle some shredded lettuce as the next layer, with a sprinkle of vegan cheese on top (as much as you want).'),
(2653, 547, '_directions_7_direction', 'field_5aec26cd305c8'),
