(2690, 549, 'directions_0_direction', 'Start by making your vegan chili. Saute vegan meat in a skillet with some olive oil. Once browned, add in your tomato paste, and your chili powder. Mix well. You can add as much chili powder as you want, and even some garlic powder!'),
