(3162, 622, 'directions_4_direction', 'Spray a large casserole dish (I used a 14 inch by 9 inch) with cooking spray. Spread about 1/2-1 cup of salsa on the bottom of the dish. Layer tortillas on top, followed by 1 to 1 and 1/2 cups of your chicken mixture. Layer with cheese shreds. Repeat layers starting with salsa, ending with cheese.'),
