(5709, 865, 'directions_6_direction', 'Cool cakes on a rack before frosting. When ready to frost, place the bottom cake round on a flat surface. Put a thin layer of frosting on the top of the bottom layer of the cake. Take your cherry pie filling, and spread a layer on top of the thin frosting layer. Place the 2nd cake round on top of the cherry pie layer.'),
(5710, 865, '_directions_6_direction', 'field_5aec26cd305c8'),
