(815, 3, '2019-07-30 02:06:31', '2019-07-30 02:06:31', '<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><p>Anyone that knows me knows that I LOVE cheese. This was my hardest obstacle to overcome going vegan. After trying every vegan cheese on the market, here are my favorites! And I can honestly tell you being Vegan has never been easier!</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Shredded Cheese</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://followyourheart.com/vegan-cheese/\">Follow Your Heart Shredded Cheese</a>:  1 of my go to brands for cheddar, mozzarella, fiesta blended shredded cheese. Works great in pretty much all recipes. Can be found at most grocery stores and Whole Foods.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://sodeliciousdairyfree.com/product_groups/dairy-free-shreds\">So Delicious Cheese Shreds</a>: This brand is probably my favorite for Shredded Cheese. It melts the closest to regular cheese that I have seen. I love their mozzarella, cheddar, and monterey jack blend!</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wayfarefoods.com/\">Wayfare Cheddar Cheese Dip:</a></li>\n<li> </li>\n</ul>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'What are good vegan cheese substitutes?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '509-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-07-30 02:06:31', '2019-07-30 02:06:31', '', 509, 'https://www.veganandcheese.com/509-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
